能使用了，有些没有邮件通知，朋友们都可去看看。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-family: PingFangSC-light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1.1px;text-align: start;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">链接 ：https://aistudio.google.com/</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="242" data-backw="562" data-height="1286" data-imgfileid="100074098" data-ratio="0.4305555555555556" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="2986" style="border-radius: 18px;width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7Rb7ZpuicwzTcLhMWoNLeQZsibwvbQ8wzyGFv1WRDH3PvvAvwic70b8yib6rMdUlyLsiaa3ZGhVXiacJNbA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin: 24px 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">Gemini 1.5 Pro 最大的特点就是10M 上下文与多模态理解相互搭配，实现超强的检索和学习能力，我们也就围绕这两点，问了他五个问题</span><br></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-family: PingFangSC-light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1.1px;text-align: start;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-family: PingFangSC-light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1.1px;text-align: start;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><div style="margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;font-size: 16px;"><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="will-