二：20篇论文，哪篇更有价值？</strong></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><p style="margin: 24px 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">我们选取了20篇神经网络相关的英文学术文章。Gemini 不仅能够对各种细节问题对答如流，而且还能够非常有条理有逻辑地整理出最具参考价值的学术论文。</span></p><p style="margin: 24px 8px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">各位研究学者们再也不用熬夜看文献写报告了！你们的头发有救啦！</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;"></span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="1252" data-backw="562" data-height="2265" data-imgfileid="100074101" data-ratio="2.2271386430678466" data-type="png" data-w="1017" data-width="1017" style="border-radius: 18px;width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7Rb7ZpuicwzTcLhMWoNLeQZseRg67Uv1FibrjzSctkxQqFdox5rmKNY2WtO1ABqA6YUADibibjhpyVsFg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-family: PingFangSC-light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1.1px;text-align: start;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-b